OL,3,CRapist and stalker asked to 'call mum
OL,4,Cand dad' when arrested
OL,6,FThe moment Jack-Leland Webster was
OL,7,Farrested, caught on bodyworn cameras
OL,8,Fby Greater Manchester Police.
OL,10,FA man convicted of stalking,
OL,11,Fstrangling and raping a woman asked if
OL,12,Fhe could call his mum and dad while
OL,13,Fbeing arrested for his crimes.
OL,15,FJack-Leland Webster attacked and raped
OL,16,Fhis victim, threatening to kill her
OL,17,Fbefore then stalking her while on bail
OL,18,Fthrough hundreds of fake social media
OL,19,Faccounts.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
