PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775751065
OL,3,CRapist and stalker asked to 'call mum
OL,4,Cand dad' when arrested
OL,6,FOn one occasion, after blocking the
OL,7,Fdoorway to her flat and stopping her
OL,8,Ffrom leaving, Webster - previously
OL,9,FJack Malone - got on top of the
OL,10,Fvictim, strangled her and told her:
OL,11,F"Don't make me kill you. If you do,
OL,12,FI'll have to kill myself so we can be
OL,13,Fdead together." He then sexually
OL,14,Fassaulted her.
OL,16,FWhen arrested at his flat in
OL,17,FManchester, Webster was seen opening
OL,18,Fthe door and looking shocked as
OL,19,Fofficers arrested him on suspicion of
OL,20,Ffalse imprisonment, rape and non-fatal
OL,21,Fstrangulation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775751065
OL,3,CRapist and stalker asked to 'call mum
OL,4,Cand dad' when arrested
OL,6,FHe was heard asking: "Can I phone my
OL,7,Fmum and dad please?", before then
OL,8,Fbeing heard to say: "I don't share the
OL,9,Fsame name as my mum" and that he would
OL,10,Fwant to "tell her".
OL,12,FManchester Crown Court heard the
OL,13,Fvictim had been in communication with
OL,14,Fher ex in June 2024, after he had
OL,15,Freached out to tell her he was
OL,16,Fconcerned as Webster had been
OL,17,Fimpersonating him to message the
OL,18,Fvictim and test her loyalty throughout
OL,19,Ftheir relationship.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775751065
OL,3,CRapist and stalker asked to 'call mum
OL,4,Cand dad' when arrested
OL,6,FAfter assaulting and strangling her,
OL,7,FWebster, from Leicester, was arrested
OL,8,Fbut then broke his bail conditions by
OL,9,Fpurchasing fake social media accounts
OL,10,Fto follow and contact the victim and
OL,11,Fher friends and family.
OL,13,FOn one occasion, the victim was
OL,14,Ffollowed by more than 100 accounts on
OL,15,Fa social media platform in a matter of
OL,16,Fseconds. Webster also sent her
OL,17,Fmessages whilst pretending to be her
OL,18,Fex-partner.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775751065
OL,3,CRapist and stalker asked to 'call mum
OL,4,Cand dad' when arrested
OL,6,FDuring interviews, Webster denied all
OL,7,Fcharges against him and Greater
OL,8,FManchester Police (GMP) said "he
OL,9,Fshowed no remorse throughout the
OL,10,Finvestigation and treated it as a
OL,11,Fgame".
OL,13,FWhen an officer tried to arrange his
OL,14,Fsecond interview, he was obstructive
OL,15,Fand told the officer to "pick me up
OL,16,Ffrom KFC" and "catch me if you can".
OL,18,FWhen he arrived for his interview, he
OL,19,Fbrought with him a book on how to be a
OL,20,Fgood debater and said this was to give
OL,21,Fan idea of how his interview would go.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775751065
OL,3,CRapist and stalker asked to 'call mum
OL,4,Cand dad' when arrested
OL,6,FWebster, who was convicted following a
OL,7,Ftrial, was sentenced to nine years and
OL,8,Ffive months in prison. He has also
OL,9,Fbeen given an indefinite restraining
OL,10,Forder.
OL,12,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,13,FConstable Lucy Hatton said: "Thank you
OL,14,Fto the brave victim in coming forward
OL,15,Fand reporting the abuse Webster
OL,16,Fsubjected her to, as well as her
OL,17,Fcontinued support throughout the
OL,18,Finvestigation, which allowed the
OL,19,Fpolice to safeguard her appropriately.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775751065
OL,3,CRapist and stalker asked to 'call mum
OL,4,Cand dad' when arrested
OL,6,F"Jack-Leland Webster (formerly Jack
OL,7,FMalone) is a very dangerous individual
OL,8,Fwho was rightly remanded in custody
OL,9,Ffollowing a prolonged stalking and
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse campaign where he
OL,11,Fbreached bail conditions multiple
OL,12,Ftimes.
OL,14,F"I hope this sentence offers some
OL,15,Freassurance for other victims of
OL,16,Fstalking and sexual offences.
OL,18,F"We take all reports of stalking, rape
OL,19,Fand sexual assaults very seriously and
OL,20,Fwill pursue these offenders and bring
OL,21,Fthem to justice."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
